title: Private Studio!
posting_body: Large secluded studio, very private, located on the lower level of the front yard, far from street.
Quiet space surrounded by nature in the quiet residential neighborhood.
Kitchenette with hot plate and microwave.
Please introduce yourself and specify moving in date, how long and as well as who is in your tenancy (single, couple, partners, roommates, pets?)
Please provide phone number and when is a best time to call.
